commit.message:
fnmatch.c: Make the note about the origins of this file more accurate...

* fnmatch.c: Make the note about the origins of this file more
accurate, at least until we can sync with glibc.
* getopt.c: Ditto.
* getopt1.c: Ditto.
* md5.c: Ditto.
* obstack.c: Ditto.

From-SVN: r38550
